∀ {a : ℕ → ℝ} {b : ℕ → ℕ} (n : ℕ) (f : ℝ[X]),
  (∀ i, b i ≠ b (i + 1) ∧ b i > 0) →
  (1 - X) ^ n * f = 1 + ∑ i in Finset.range n, a i * X ^ (b i) →
  f.eval 1 = (∏ i in Finset.range n, b i) / n.factorial

∀ {n : ℕ} {a : Fin n → ℝ} {b : Fin n → ℕ} (h : Function.Injective b)
  (f : ℝ[X]) (hf : (1 - X) ^ n * f = 1 + ∑ i, C (a i) * X ^ (b i)),
  eval 1 f = (∏ i, b i) / n.factorial

∀ {n : ℕ} {a : Fin n → ℝ} {b : Fin n → ℕ},
  (∀ i j, i ≠ j → b i ≠ b j) →
  ∃ f : Polynomial ℝ, (1 - Polynomial.X) ^ n * f = 1 + ∑ i, a i * Polynomial.X ^ (b i) →
  f.eval 1 = (Finset.prod Finset.univ b) / (Nat.factorial n)

∀ {n : ℕ} {a : Fin n → ℝ} {b : Fin n → ℕ} (h : Function.Injective b) (f : ℝ[X]),
  (1 - Polynomial.X) ^ n * f = 1 + ∑ i, a i * Polynomial.X ^ b i →
    f.eval 1 = (∏ i, b i) / Nat.factorial n

∀ {n : ℕ} {a : Fin n → ℝ} {b : Fin n → ℕ} (h_distinct : ∀ i j, i ≠ j → b i ≠ b j)
  (h_pos : ∀ i, 0 < b i) (f : ℝ[X]), 
  (1 - X) ^ n * f = 1 + ∑ i, a i * X ^ b i →
  f.eval 1 = (∏ i, b i) / (n.factorial : ℝ)

∀ {n : ℕ} {a : Fin n → ℝ} {b : Fin n → ℕ},
  Function.Injective b →
    (∃ f : Polynomial ℝ, (1 - Polynomial.X) ^ n * f = 1 + ∑ i, a i * Polynomial.X ^ (b i)) →
      Polynomial.eval 1 f = (∏ i, b i) / Nat.factorial n

∀ {a : Fin n → ℝ} {b : Fin n → ℕ} (hb : ∀ i j, i ≠ j → b i ≠ b j) (f : ℝ[X]),
  ((1 - Polynomial.X) ^ n) * f = 1 + ∑ i, Polynomial.C (a i) * Polynomial.X ^ (b i) →
    Polynomial.eval 1 f = ∏ i, b i / Nat.factorial n

∀ {a : ℕ → ℝ} {b : ℕ → ℕ} {f : ℝ[X]} {n : ℕ},
  (∀ i j, i ≠ j → b i ≠ b j) →
    ((1 - Polynomial.X) ^ n * f = 1 + ∑ i in Finset.range n, (a i) * Polynomial.X ^ (b i)) →
      f.eval 1 = (∏ i in Finset.range n, b i) / (n.factorial)

∀ {R : Type u_1} [inst : CommRing R] (a : ℕ → R) (b : ℕ → ℕ) (n : ℕ),
  (Polynomial.prod (Finset.range n) fun k => Polynomial.X - (1 : Polynomial R)) * (Polynomial.C (a 0) + Polynomial.sum (Finset.range n) fun i => Polynomial.C (a i) * Polynomial.X ^ b i) =
    Polynomial.C 1 → Polynomial.eval 1 (Polynomial.prod (Finset.range n) fun k => Polynomial.X - (1 : Polynomial R)) = (b 0 * b 1 * b 2 * ... * b (n - 1)) / Nat.factorial n

∀ {n : ℕ} {a : Fin n → ℝ} {b : Fin n → ℕ} (h_distinct : ∀ i j, i ≠ j → b i ≠ b j) (f : ℝ[X]), 
  ((1 - X) ^ n * f = 1 + ∑ i, Polynomial.monomial (b i) (a i)) →
    f.eval 1 = (∏ i, b i) / n.factorial
